            "text_bPbJ4x": {
              "type": "text",
              "name": "t:names.text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>The pyjama top isn't really for bedtime. Rather, it is a light, unstructured jacket, with some of the trappings of old-fashioned jim-jams. It has an open collar, which falls low, and is suited well to being worn in a louche and laid-back manner — over a t-shirt, say, or light shirt — ideally in spring and summer.</p>",
